# .lightning_studio/.studiorc
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  Sourced by every new shell Lightning opens in this Studio. We use it to
#  export the paths and env vars that the user normally relies on `nanobot.env`
#  for, so manual commands typed in the web terminal Just Work.
